data.description: To No Fault of the Property or the Seller, this great Property is back on the Market. Here is that perfect 15 acres with a very cool open concept 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, 2 car garage Home is set back off the highway, You never even hear the hwy. There is a very warm comfortable feeling about this place, come and make it what you want. Take notice of the old Barn & Pens, that with a lil work could be ready for your Livestock. Ag Exemption already in place, just looking for a new family. Plenty of space, Bring your Horses, Dirt Bikes,,,, and enjoy this neat property. There is a good Pond, just needs rain to bring it back to life. Lots of Potential in a great area. Just south of I-20, north of Morgan Mill. Don't let this one slip away.
